snippet.title: LOVE LIAR DAMIEN - DATE PART 1, FULL VERSION.
snippet.description:
P/S : Aira is MC's name. 

PHEWWW. After a few days keep farming the gems, finally I able to unlock Damien's first date!!

LOVE LIAR DAMIEN - DATE PART 1, FULL VERSION. 

Love Liar is now available on Apple App Store : https://apps.apple.com/my/app/love-liar-secret-romance/id1645805999

Love Liar is now available on Google Play Store : https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.storytaco.p24client&hl=en&gl=US

ALL MEMBERS CRITICAL PARTS IS COMPLETE. You can check it out at my Youtube channel for more details. 
Their dates (Kasey, Tiffany) & ending parts (Damien, Tiffany, Kasey) - SOON. 
TIMOTHY & DAMIEN's dates part is COMPLETE. 

Reminder as usual, slow updates for the next updates related to LOVE LIAR. About LUNA SONATA....maybe later since I wanna give a try complete LOVE LIAR members dates and endings first.
